{"tid":864984,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[TCG] Pokemon TCG Online (3)","createTime":"2018-10-16T15:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T04:37:30.000Z","uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05821110dd80b080ee7d75cc5f410c76ac3c5d48","tid":864984,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXyGFfA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXyGFfA.jpg&h=47a7ffc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n召喚所有鐘意PKM TCG嘅老手/新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDownload Link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/play-online/download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.com%2Fus%2Fpokemon-tcg%2Fplay-online%2Fdownload%2F&d=giYS6%2FePNWc1CPnj5jCptQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a7557410\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/play-online/download/</a><br />\n可以喺Tablet/PC度玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/play-online/what-is-tcgo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.com%2Fus%2Fpokemon-tcg%2Fplay-online%2Fwhat-is-tcgo%2F&d=giYS6%2FePNWc1CPnj5jCptQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a9e78f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/play-online/what-is-tcgo/</a><br />\nGame入面一開始都會有教學內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n卡牌種類：<br />\n主要分三大類<br />\n1)Pok&eacute;mon<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNqmFf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNqmFf8.jpg&h=98b6b463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2)Trainer [item, supporter, stadium, tools]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx61FgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx61FgM.jpg&h=835f8295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbRH896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbRH896.jpg&h=4aae5b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVNPO98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVNPO98.jpg&h=a4f0e68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XS1tkgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXS1tkgO.jpg&h=d563a27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3)Energy<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/123746_83692ce1b87b3c20a60e985db94100ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F123746_83692ce1b87b3c20a60e985db94100ac.jpg&h=0817a386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ. Online版點課金？<br />\nA.現時所有美版產品入面都有個對應嗰樣產品嘅code，入咗code就可以喺入面玩/trade野。<br />\n<br />\nQ.邊度可以就咁買code?<br />\nA.可以上淘寶 / Ebay / 直接同香港啲players收。<br />\n<br />\nQ.現時咩deck最好用？<br />\nA.可以等其他高手巴絲答你，或者上YouTube打PKM TCG deck大把鬼佬YouTuber教大家；<br />\n亦都可以上limitlesstcg望下有咩上位deck。<br />\n<br />\nQ.實體卡好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想入坑玩實卡/瘋狂收藏，邊度有得賣？<br />\nA.主要都係去長沙灣天悅, 太子 pc, 油麻地 tcge, 荃灣通用, 觀塘 Card Hero,<br />\n連鎖店有 奇趣天地 同 玩具反斗城。<br />\n<br />\nQ.咩係GX Pokemon/Prism Star?<br />\nA.GX Pokemon有招GX技，成鋪入面每個player只可以用一次GX技，而打敗GX寵可以一次拎兩張Prize Card。Prism Star咭就係每款只可以有一張喺deck入面，用完放落Lost Zone。<br />\n<br />\nQ.新手玩online版點上手好？<br />\nA.打trainer challenge 解鎖啲卡，<br />\n再用儲返嚟嘅coins買副蜥蜴王[Leaf Charge] /烈咬陸鯊[Mach Strike] theme deck<br />\n打versus入面嘅theme繼續儲下coin。<br />\n<br />\n希望其他巴絲繼續補充常見問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649bfcddd884b5744f55b064b525c90953286234","tid":864984,"uid":29211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:22:57.000Z","msg":"幫手推下post"},{"pid":"5ddb042be574244